        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-4">Up and running in 4 steps</h2>
        <p class="text-warm-gray text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">From zero to your first validated mapping in under two minutes.</p>
